            <title>[PIG-2702] Make Pig local mode (and tests) faster by working around the hard coded sleep(5000) in hadoop&apos;s JobControl</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2702</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;the JobControl class polls the jobs statuses with a hard coded sleep(5000) making every job take a minimum of 5 seconds.&lt;br/&gt;
